What does the rect function do?
  the rect function allows us to draw a square on a grid in processing.

What does the rectMode function do?
  the rectMode function allows us to choose how we draw the squares on the grid,
    - ie with corners, width/length etc.

What is a pixel?
  a pixel is a tiny illuminated area on a screen, one part of the whole

What is HSB?
  HSB is hue, saturation, and brightness
